00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:51.930
The more mass you start with,
the more energy you get.

00:09:51.930 --> 00:09:54.810
Well, my equation
shows that sugar can be

00:09:54.810 --> 00:09:56.880
converted into ethyl alcohol.

00:09:56.880 --> 00:10:01.770
The more sugar you start with,
the more alcohol you get.

