human race to survive attacks

00:12:35.700 --> 00:12:39.000
that would have otherwise
neatly killed us off--

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:42.330
and ultimately, go on
to invent cool stuff

00:12:42.330 --> 00:12:46.595
