00:19:49.310 --> 00:19:52.400
Laborers would drink gallons
of the stuff every day

00:19:52.400 --> 00:19:54.800
while they were sweating
away their electrolytes.

00:19:54.800 --> 00:19:57.500
It was the original
sports drink, really.

