the type of alcohol we drink.

00:20:05.870 --> 00:20:07.370
Now, there's lots
of other alcohols.

00:20:07.370 --> 00:20:13.460
There's methanol, isopropyl
alcohol, butanol, amyl alcohol.

00:20:13.460 --> 00:20:16.580
But the only one we
drink is ethyl alcohol.

00:20:16.580 --> 00:20:19.070
