00:21:32.430 --> 00:21:37.890
So ethanol is a volatile,
flammable, colorless liquid

00:21:37.890 --> 00:21:40.987
with the structural
formula CH3 CH2 OH.

00:21:40.987 --> 00:21:42.570
Now, best known as
the type of alcohol

00:21:42.570 --> 00:21:44.400
found in alcoholic
beverages, it is also

00:21:44.400 --> 00:21:48.210
used in thermometers, as
a solvent, and as a fuel.

00:21:48.210 --> 00:21:52.800
Ethyl alcohol can cause alcohol
intoxication when consumed.

00:21:52.800 --> 00:21:55.470
It is one of the oldest
recreational drugs still used

00:21:55.470 --> 00:21:58.500
by humans with significant
psychoactive effects.

00:21:58.500 --> 00:22:00.330
In common usage, it
is often referred

00:22:00.330 --> 00:22:05.110
to simply as alcohol,
liquor, or hooch.

00:22:05.110 --> 00:22:05.610
Yeah.

00:22:05.610 --> 00:22:08.580
No thank you, Wikipedia.

00:22:08.580 --> 00:22:12.060
So ethanol is
volatile, That means

00:22:12.060 --> 00:22:14.157
it boils at a low temperature.

00:22:14.157 --> 00:22:15.240
You need to remember that.

00:22:15.240 --> 00:22:16.230
