00:32:14.570 --> 00:32:17.960
And often, alcohol was involved,
so this was a perfect fit

00:32:17.960 --> 00:32:20.489
for me right out of college.

00:32:20.489 --> 00:32:21.780
KATE HOOVER: I just love booze.

00:32:21.780 --> 00:32:25.130
No, I also went to school
for musical theater.

00:32:25.130 --> 00:32:27.839
I never really had acappella
training, but I just--

