00:32:39.110 --> 00:32:40.110
SPEAKER: It's fantastic.

00:32:40.110 --> 00:32:42.940
NICOLE DIMATTEI:
It's a unique talent

00:32:42.940 --> 00:32:44.579
and actually hard to find.

00:32:44.579 --> 00:32:46.620
We've been casting this
show now for three years,

00:32:46.620 --> 00:32:48.440
and we have four
versions of the show.

00:32:48.440 --> 00:32:53.900
So we have a rum show, a brunch
show, and a Christmas show.

00:32:53.900 --> 00:32:56.810
