stand and sing their solo

00:33:04.610 --> 00:33:07.010
with an orchestra behind them.

00:33:07.010 --> 00:33:08.330
That's not this at all.

00:33:08.330 --> 00:33:10.760
You have to be able to hold
your own part while people

00:33:10.760 --> 00:33:14.070
