Which has got to save
money but be frustrating?

00:33:20.090 --> 00:33:21.048
ANTHONY CAPORALE: That.

00:33:21.048 --> 00:33:21.984
Both of those things.

00:33:21.984 --> 00:33:22.525
SPEAKER: Yes.

00:33:22.525 --> 00:33:24.000
Exactly.

